reviews.customers_say: Customers love the sweater's design, particularly the flower sleeves, and appreciate its soft, fuzzy texture that feels nice on the skin.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect sweater
items.body: Absolutely beautiful. Soooo soft and washes so nicely. Fit perfect Read more
items.author: Tami Angel Decker

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful, Comfortable, and Great Quality!
items.body: I purchased the SHENHE Women’s Floral Pattern Crewneck Long Sleeve, and I’m genuinely impressed with it. The top has great wrinkle resistance, which means it still looks neat even after a long day of wear. The material thickness is perfect, not flimsy at all, but still lightweight enough to feel breathable. When it comes to value for money, this piece is a winner; it looks and feels more expensive than it is. I’ve worn and washed it multiple times, and the durability is excellent with no fading, loose threads, or stretching. It also scores high on washability, it washes well, keeps its shape, and dries quickly. The overall weight of the top is light and comfortable, making it great for layering or wearing on its own. Definitely a stylish and reliable addition to my wardrobe! Read more
items.author: Save and Fancy

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute and comfortable but pilling will be present after first wash.
items.body: This is a very comfy and warm sweater. I love the flower sleeves, they are so soft. After washing, I notice that the sweater pilled a lot, making the sweater look old. Read more
items.author: LD Power

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect fit and texture
items.body: Wow I am impressed! I ordered for the cute colors and pattern but I love this sweater. Warm without causing sweat, soft as butter on the skin, color spot on. I’m so happy. The length was just right not too long or short. I’m 5’1” curvy 177 lbs. I wear 38DD and I chose a large. Everything sits just right. The price is well worth the fit and comfort. Feels thin but gives warmth. I bought this for family Christmas get together at my sons house that I’m always freezing at and I think I’m gonna be good. To note I have sensory issues with many sweaters but this one feels nice on the skin. Read more
items.author: Mary E. Herman

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adorable and super soft.
items.body: Adorable and super soft. I could size-up for the more chunky sweater look but the XL fits nicely. Plus, the arms are roomy and long enough for my thicker and longer arms. More pricey than I usually spend but worth it! Read more
items.author: Cathy

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sweet sweater for Fall
items.body: Perfect sweater! Soft and very cute. Order a size down and it’ll fit great. Read more
items.author: Virginia Pageturner

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this sweater!
items.body: This sweater is great. So soft- great quality. Might run a little big, I typically wear a M but ordered a small and it fits great! 5-4” 135 for reference. Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Nope
items.body: I’m only given this one star unfortunately. I absolutely love this sweater and thought it was so beautiful but was only able to wear it once. As soon as I washed it following the instructions it became very pilly and looks terrible. Read more
items.author: Laurie M

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Plum Purple, Blue, Floral Hot Pink, Deep Brown, Apricot, Floral Khaki, Dusty Blue, Floral Rust Brown, Floral Dusty Pink, Flower Green, Mocha Brown, Floral Green, Flower Grey, Flower Khaki. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
